# Kanban Workflow

Stories live in `docs/kanban/` with folders: **future**, **unplanned**, **planned**, **doing**, **done**.

## Future vs roadmap

- **`future/`** — Investigations and ideas **before** they are roadmap items. Filenames are **`slug.md`** only (**no `NN-` priority prefix**). Not ordered; no unplanned gates until promoted.
- **Roadmap flow:** **unplanned → planned → doing → done**. Skipping **planned** requires explicit team agreement (trivial fixes only).

## Roadmap and priority

- The **ordered roadmap** is in **`docs/kanban/unplanned/`**.
- Roadmap filenames use **`NN-slug.md`**; **`NN`** is a **globally unique** story id. On the roadmap (`unplanned/`), **lower `NN` = higher priority** within the current queue (see `docs/kanban/README.md`). Work through lower numbers first unless the story is verification-only or explicitly deferred (see tier in each file).
- The same **`NN-slug.md`** name is **moved** between **unplanned**, **planned**, **doing**, and **done**; sequence does not change.
- Promoting **`future/slug.md`** → **`unplanned/NN-slug.md`**: assign the next free **global `NN`**, add unplanned sections (see `docs/kanban/README.md`).

## Phases (short)

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| **future** | Raw investigations, ideas, spikes — **`slug.md`**, no `NN-` prefix; not build-ready; promote to **unplanned** when scoped. |
| **unplanned** | High-level intent, state, relationships, **goals**, acceptance, spec refs, **risks / notes**—not build-ready. |
| **planned** | Above plus impact analysis, **Tasks**, tests to add, docs/specs to update, optional **Notes**—still pre-code. |
| **doing** | Active implementation; tick tasks; add **Build notes**. |
| **done** | All tasks `[x]`, acceptance met, **tests passing**. |

## Gate rules

**Future → unplanned:** Team agrees the item is roadmap-ready; rename to **`NN-slug.md`**, move to **`unplanned/`**, add **Sequence**, **Tier**, and full unplanned sections per `docs/kanban/README.md`.

**Unplanned → planned:** summary, current state, relationships, **goals**, acceptance criteria, spec references, and **risks / notes** are complete. No detailed task grid yet (that is added in planned).

**Planned → doing:** impact analysis, Tasks, Tests to add, Documentation/specs lists are filled in.

**Doing → done:** every task complete, build notes as needed, required test commands green per `AGENTS.md`.

**Deprecated:** `docs/kanban/backlog/` — use **`planned/`** instead.

Full entry/exit criteria and templates: **`docs/kanban/README.md`**.

Skills: **`kestrel-kanban-story-create`**, **`kestrel-kanban-story-migrate`** in `.cursor/skills/`.

Subagents: **`.cursor/agents/kanban-*.md`**.
